
# CTNS #

Basic tasks:
 1. algebra -> <n|ctns>, <ctns1|ctns2>, <ctns1|H|ctns2>, etc.
 2. sampling -> |<n|ctns>|^2
 3. IO

Initialization:
 1. from SCI wavefunction
 2. variational optimization

Efficiency:
 1. use symmetry  
 2. parallelization
 
Description of files:

